VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT <WebView[^>]*javaScriptEnabled\s*=\s*\{?true\}?
WHEN EXPR MISSING:ShouldOverrideUrlLoading|NavigationDelegate|allowList|trustedOrigins && MISSING:test|example
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects JavaScript-enabled React Native WebView usage.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for WebView JavaScript Enabled.
